	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; padding-left: 45px;">How do I create my character profile with Magelo Sync?</div>	
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:10px;">
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/website/shared/right_menu/support_icone_off.png?v=21" height="15" style="position: absolute; top:0px; left:0px;" width="33" class="png32" /><img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/website/localized/picto/eq_faq_icone.png?v=21" height="24" style="position: absolute;top:-17px; left:4px;" width="24" class="png32" />	</div>
	<hr class="line">
	<br>
	
	
	<div>1. <b class="strong">Run the &#147;Magelo Sync&#148; program and log in</b> using your Magelo username and password. If you do not have one yet, you can register for a Magelo account here.<br/>
<br/>
2. <b class="strong">Choose your game from the games list</b> by clicking on the icon. This will launch the game software. If it&#146;s the first time you use Magelo Sync you will need to launch your game manually if it&#146;s not started already.<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/eq/faq/myCharacter_21a.jpg?v=2289" align="absmiddle" border="0" /><br/>
<br/>
3. <b class="strong">Log into the game</b>. Magelo Sync will automatically detect your character once it has logged in. Press the &#147;<b class="strong">Sync Now!</b>&#148; button to sync it. If the auto-Sync feature is enabled, it will automatically Sync the character information without using the button.<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/eq/faq/myCharacter_21b.jpg?v=2289" align="absmiddle" border="0" /><br/>
<br/>
4.<b class="strong">Your character profile has been successfully created</b>! You can view it by clicking on its name in Magelo Sync. Log into your Magelo account on the website to manage it. <br/>
<br/>
Find <b class="strong">below a profile sample</b>. You just need to click on it to see the character profile in real size.<br/>
<a href='http://eq.magelo.com/profile/790513' target='blank'><br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/eq/faq/myCharacter_21c.jpg?v=2289" align="absmiddle" border="0" /></a><br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<b class="strong">The Magelo Database is accessible to you even while playing the game</b>! Information on the currently targeted NPC and the area your character is located will be shown in Magelo Sync. You may click on them for a quick lookup on information related to the particular mob. The &#147;<b class="strong">Quick Search</b>&#148; bar works also as a quick search for information in our database.<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/eq/faq/myCharacter_21d.jpg?v=2289" align="absmiddle" border="0" /><br/>
<br/>
You may press the &#147;<b class="strong">Sync Now!</b>&#148; button to <b class="strong">update your character profile whenever you wish, as many times as needed.</b><br/>
<br/>
The gold sword icon beside your character name in Magelo Sync lets you <b class="strong">view additional details such as your character&#039;s base statistics, equipment, inventory, bank and gold</b>. <br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/eq/faq/myCharacter_21e.jpg?v=2289" align="absmiddle" border="0" /><br/>
<br/>
Magelo Sync <b class="strong">fully supports multi boxing and offline characters</b>. Magelo Sync works with multiple game sessions open at the same time, saving data for additional characters in a separate tab. If you have already opened a game session, you may open another session in order to log into another account.<br/>
<br/>
Magelo Sync will also <b class="strong">link to news and announcements on the Magelo website</b>. You may click on the news tab at the top right side to open up a window to the website.<br/>
<br/>
Magelo Sync can perform its tasks automatically! Click on the &#147;<b class="strong">Settings</b>&#148; tab at the top right side to open up the Settings menu, where you can set Magelo Sync to be as automated as you would like with features such as <b class="strong">minimizing Sync at startup, auto-exporting characters, auto-launching your favorite game, auto-Sync your characters</b> and more!<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/eq/faq/myCharacter_21f.jpg?v=2289" align="absmiddle" border="0" /><br/>
<br/>
If you have problems running Magelo Sync, please let us know in our <a href='http://eq.magelo.com/forum/topics.jspa?forum=9' target='blank'>Bug Report forums</a>! A log file of the session will also help.<br/>
 <b class="strong">Press Ctrl + Shift + L to open up the log when Magelo Sync is running</b>, then copy and paste the contents into the post.<br/>
<br/>
For more information about Magelo Sync, check out <a href='http://eq.magelo.com/magelo_sync.jspa' target='blank'>this page</a>.<br/>
</div>
